    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Totally enclosed boxlike freight cars, with floor, roof, sides, and ends, usually with large doors on the sides or sides and ends.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
